    <summary>AI-native terminal manager where Claude, Codex, Gemini, and Qwen work together as a team</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[
## Termpolis

The first terminal where Claude, Codex, Gemini, and Qwen work together as a team.

Smart task routing assigns the right work to the right AI model. An intelligent conductor that knows who plays what instrument best.

### Features
- Multi-terminal sessions with split panes and workspaces
- AI swarm with smart routing — describe a task and agents collaborate automatically
- Support for Claude Code, OpenAI Codex, Gemini CLI, and Aider+Qwen
- Built-in MCP server for AI agent integration
- Command palette, prompt templates, and tab completion
- WCAG AA accessible
- Windows code signed
]]></description>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/codedev-david/termpolis/releases/tag/v1.4.1</releaseNotes>
